Invocation Name: minions alarms
des:
The Minions Alarm features a selection of fan favorite sounds from the most iconic animated characters of their generation.

Now you can wake up to the sounds of the mischievous Minions every day!

Alarms included in this pack:

“Peep Peep Peep”
“Banana!”
“Kumbaya!”
“Bello! La Lala La Lala”
“Boing Boing Boing!”
“Oh! Hello, Papaguena! Tu Le Bella Comme Le Papaya”
